          <p class="mb-4">When using our Site, you agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide accurate information when submitting venues or contact forms</li>
            <li>Use the Site only for lawful purposes</li>
            <li>Not attempt to interfere with or disrupt the Site's functionality</li>
            <li>Not scrape, copy, or reproduce our content without permission</li>
            <li>Comply with all applicable local, state, and federal laws</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
