            <li>Listings do not constitute endorsement or recommendation</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">6. Health and Safety Disclaimers</h2>
          <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Important Health Information</h3>
            <p class="text-amber-700 mb-4">
              The information on this Site is for educational purposes only and is not intended as medical advice. Please be aware:
