              <li><strong>THC Beverages:</strong> May impair judgment, coordination, and reaction time. Do not drive or operate machinery after consumption. Effects can last 2-8 hours.</li>
              <li>Both substances should be avoided by pregnant or nursing women</li>
              <li>Consult your healthcare provider before using any new substances</li>
