        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">7. Third-Party Links and Affiliate Relationships</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our Site contains links to third-party websites, including our affiliate partner Better Rhodes. Please note:
